37
00:03:39.560 --> 00:03:42.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I heard you'd seen them. so I'd like to meet—</font>

38
00:03:42.770 --> 00:03:44.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh. that's it!</font>

39
00:03:45.390 --> 00:03:47.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">New topic: "what do you look for in a crush"?</font>

40
00:03:49.900 --> 00:03:54.710
