44
00:04:11.900 --> 00:04:14.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Wh-What the hell?</font>

45
00:04:14.070 --> 00:04:16.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Brass tacks. lady.</font>

46
00:04:16.210 --> 00:04:18.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Is this romance talk the price for info?</font>

47
00:04:19.250 --> 00:04:21.540
