50
00:04:29.430 --> 00:04:30.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but we'll play along.</font>

51
00:04:32.890 --> 00:04:34.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh...</font>

52
00:04:37.090 --> 00:04:38.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's weird.</font>

53
00:04:39.530 --> 00:04:43.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's weird. That's weird. 
That's weird. That's weird.</font>

54
00:04:43.460 --> 00:04:46.240
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's weird. That's weird. 
That's weird. That's weird.</font>

55
00:04:46.240 --> 00:04:48.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's weird! That's weird! 
That's weird! That's weird!</font>

56
00:04:48.850 --> 00:04:52.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's weird! That's weird! That's weird!</font>

57
00:04:52.730 --> 00:04:55.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You came here to talk to Amo. no?!</font>

58
00:04:55.340 --> 00:05:01.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But you talk like all you 
