59
00:05:01.650 --> 00:05:03.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's weird! That's weird!</font>

60
00:05:03.950 --> 00:05:07.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo was so happy to finally 
have visitors from outside!</font>

61
00:05:07.380 --> 00:05:09.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Now you just want to <i>use</i> Amo?!</font>

62
00:05:09.200 --> 00:05:11.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well. that's not good.</font>

63
00:05:11.330 --> 00:05:15.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You don't want to see Amo 
unless you get something from Amo?!</font>

64
00:05:15.930 --> 00:05:18.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That's the worst!</font>

65
00:05:18.250 --> 00:05:22.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">At least say you came here just 
to see Amo even if it's a lie!</font>

66
00:05:23.250 --> 00:05:27.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey. sorry. I didn't phrase that right.</font>

67
00:05:29.810 --> 00:05:31.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm interested in you. girl!</font>

68
00:05:36.810 --> 00:05:39.400
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't you <i>dare</i> lie!</font>

69
00:05:40.580 --> 00:05:42.830
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo's not into you anymore!</font>

70
00:05:44.070 --> 00:05:45.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Look...</font>

71
00:05:47.280 --> 00:05:50.350
