72
00:05:51.070 --> 00:05:54.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Could you cover up a little? 
It's hard to concentrate. here.</font>

73
00:05:57.470 --> 00:06:01.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Men who complain about women's fashion...</font>

74
00:06:03.250 --> 00:06:07.030
