76
00:06:14.010 --> 00:06:17.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo won't even let you be friends!</font>

77
00:06:18.580 --> 00:06:21.080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Figured. She's a Giver.</font>

78
