81
00:06:42.460 --> 00:06:44.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">big man.</font>

82
00:06:50.470 --> 00:06:52.980
<font size="20"><b><font size="40"><font color="#e2e0e1">And Now...</font></font></b></font>

83
00:08:30.880 --> 00:08:33.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What the hell...</font>

84
00:08:35.770 --> 00:08:39.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">did you just do... to Enjin?</font>

85
00:08:43.130 --> 00:08:44.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey!</font>

86
00:08:44.490 --> 00:08:46.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You did something. right?</font>

87
00:08:46.300 --> 00:08:48.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're a Giver. aren't you?!</font>

88
00:08:48.010 --> 00:08:52.310
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And I see your boots have 
the same mark as my 3R...</font>

89
00:08:52.310 --> 00:08:55.510
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Just what the hell <i>are</i> you?!</font>

90
00:08:57.500 --> 00:09:01.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Okay! What do you look for in a crush?</font>

91
00:09:05.290 --> 00:09:07.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why don't you talk?</font>

92
00:09:07.430 --> 00:09:10.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Talking is how people communicate. you know?</font>

93
00:09:11.020 --> 00:09:15.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If only Amo talks. then you and Amo 
can't get to know each other better.</font>

94
00:09:15.950 --> 00:09:19.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">People always love talking about themselves!</font>

95
00:09:19.460 --> 00:09:23.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So it'll be more fun if you all 
talk about yourselves too!</font>

96
00:09:23.630 --> 00:09:28.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo doesn't get many visitors. so Amo 
wants to enjoy talking with all of you!</font>

97
00:09:29.880 --> 00:09:31.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well...</font>

98
00:09:31.500 --> 00:09:34.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maybe not the party poopers.</font>

99
00:09:34.810 --> 00:09:36.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No way.</font>

100
00:09:36.450 --> 00:09:39.200
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's no way I can talk to this girl...</font>

101
00:09:44.020 --> 00:09:45.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I think I'm gettin' it.</font>

102
00:09:46.840 --> 00:09:50.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You only listen to people who play along 
with your topic of choice</font>

103
00:09:50.190 --> 00:09:53.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">or are actively tryin' to bring it down.</font>

104
00:09:54.510 --> 00:09:58.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Which means I bet you'll 
hear me loud and clear—</font>

105
00:09:58.290 --> 00:09:59.410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You cow.</font>

106
00:09:59.750 --> 00:10:03.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm not gonna listen to any more 
of your creepy chatter. dumbass.</font>

107
00:10:03.050 --> 00:10:05.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I dunno how you did that back there.</font>

108
00:10:05.330 --> 00:10:09.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but if that's how you're gonna treat Enjin.</font>

109
00:10:09.340 --> 00:10:12.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">then I don't give a damn 
about the Sphere anymore.</font>

110
00:10:12.920 --> 00:10:15.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I see an enemy. and I'm gonna crush it.</font>

111
00:10:16.150 --> 00:10:17.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Zanka.</font>

112
00:10:17.260 --> 00:10:19.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How?</font>

113
00:10:22.380 --> 00:10:25.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How could you say all those mean things?</font>

114
00:10:26.540 --> 00:10:30.940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo didn't do anything bad!</font>

115
00:10:31.260 --> 00:10:34.630
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So mean... So mean...</font>

116
00:10:35.320 --> 00:10:38.960
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo is so. so...</font>

117
00:10:40.880 --> 00:10:42.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">wounded.</font>

118
00:10:49.190 --> 00:10:52.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What the hell?! You're on our side. Delmon!</font>

119
00:10:52.090 --> 00:10:54.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She usin' her power to control you?</font>

120
00:10:54.650 --> 00:10:59.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How <i>dare</i> you hurt her!</font>

121
00:11:00.100 --> 00:11:01.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You bastards!</font>

122
00:11:01.520 --> 00:11:03.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If you do anything else to hurt her.</font>

123
00:11:03.910 --> 00:11:05.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">you'll get no mercy from me!</font>

124
00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:06.730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Squee.</font>

125
00:11:07.310 --> 00:11:10.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She is the reason I fight!</font>

126
00:11:10.930 --> 00:11:14.650
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I will protect her! That is my sacred duty!</font>

127
00:11:14.980 --> 00:11:16.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No.</font>

128
00:11:16.460 --> 00:11:18.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He's not being controlled.</font>

129
00:11:18.460 --> 00:11:19.880
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He means it!</font>

130
00:11:19.880 --> 00:11:22.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I've spent enough time with him to know.</font>

131
00:11:22.230 --> 00:11:24.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey. Hang on a minute.</font>

132
00:11:24.540 --> 00:11:26.750
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">This doesn't make sense.</font>

133
00:11:27.140 --> 00:11:29.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What's going on here. then?!</font>

134
00:11:31.990 --> 00:11:36.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Aw. you didn't realize?</font>

135
00:11:39.040 --> 00:11:43.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Big man here has been Amo's fan for ages.</font>

136
00:11:43.470 --> 00:11:44.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Delmon has?</font>

137
00:11:44.670 --> 00:11:45.980
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Since when?</font>

138
00:11:45.980 --> 00:11:47.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">No.</font>

139
00:11:47.850 --> 00:11:51.440
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Delmon wouldn't attack his own team 
just because he had a crush.</font>

140
00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:54.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You still don't get it...</font>

141
00:11:54.430 --> 00:11:58.840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Big man would gladly betray 
you all just to help Amo.</font>

142
00:11:58.840 --> 00:12:00.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But of course he would!</font>

143
00:12:00.910 --> 00:12:04.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo hasn't done anything wrong...</font>

144
00:12:05.770 --> 00:12:10.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo just wanted to talk. and you ruined it!</font>

145
00:12:13.350 --> 00:12:17.920
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Vital Instrument—Ookiku Naare.</font>

146
00:12:21.690 --> 00:12:24.060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We just came here to get information.</font>

147
00:12:24.950 --> 00:12:27.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but we got more than we bargained for.</font>

148
00:12:29.460 --> 00:12:33.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Why does it always turn into a fight?</i></font>

149
00:12:33.700 --> 00:12:36.490
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><i>Is this my fault too?!</i></font>

150
00:12:37.150 --> 00:12:39.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It is your fault.</font>

151
00:12:43.190 --> 00:12:45.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Child with the blood of a criminal.</font>

152
00:12:45.760 --> 00:12:46.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Filth.</font>

153
00:12:46.900 --> 00:12:50.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Your filth pollutes everything around you.</font>

154
00:12:50.430 --> 00:12:52.000
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Send the filth to the Pit.</font>

155
00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:53.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Send the filth to the Pit.</font>

156
00:12:53.280 --> 00:12:54.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Send the filth to the Pit.</font>

157
00:12:54.590 --> 00:12:58.970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Send the filth to the Pit.</font>

158
00:12:59.290 --> 00:13:01.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh. I know!</font>

159
00:13:01.040 --> 00:13:08.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's another fan of Amo here. isn't there?</font>

160
00:13:08.350 --> 00:13:13.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What Amo wants is for everyone to 
stay and have lots of fun talking.</font>

161
00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:20.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But... if anyone else says 
something to ruin the fun.</font>

162
00:13:25.200 --> 00:13:29.040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">my fan might just have to punish that someone!</font>

163
00:13:47.220 --> 00:13:49.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You... Apostles...</font>

164
00:13:51.470 --> 00:13:53.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What are you doing here?!</font>

165
00:13:56.650 --> 00:13:58.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Get your head in the game!</font>

166
00:14:07.700 --> 00:14:11.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're not supposed to dodge my watering.</font>

167
00:14:12.740 --> 00:14:15.590
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That vital instrument ties back 
to Delmon's past.</font>

168
00:14:15.590 --> 00:14:20.420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It came from his desire to see 
his plants grow big and strong.</font>

169
00:14:20.420 --> 00:14:25.800
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So anything hit with the water 
it spouts ends up growin'. right?</font>

170
00:14:26.630 --> 00:14:30.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Yes. It controls the fluid 
content in the target.</font>

171
00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:35.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It can force it to absorb it like a sponge 
and blow it up like a balloon.</font>

172
00:14:36.150 --> 00:14:40.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But what happens to a balloon 
that takes in too much water?</font>

173
00:14:44.470 --> 00:14:45.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It pops.</font>

174
00:14:48.030 --> 00:14:52.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm betting he "watered" Enjin from behind.</font>

175
00:14:53.060 --> 00:14:59.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">A big splash like that... 
How'd he do it without Enjin noticin'?</font>

176
00:14:59.520 --> 00:15:03.010
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He can change the nozzle setting 
for different uses.</font>

177
00:15:04.070 --> 00:15:08.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It appears he used 
the "silent nozzle" this time.</font>

178
00:15:08.760 --> 00:15:12.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He'd never used it on a person before.</font>

179
00:15:13.260 --> 00:15:15.050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That woman is definitely...</font>

180
00:15:17.190 --> 00:15:18.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Hey. listen.</font>

181
00:15:19.500 --> 00:15:24.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's a lot I don't get about this.
but what we need to do is get Delmon to chill.</font>

182
00:15:24.960 --> 00:15:27.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Gotta take care of problems quick.</font>

183
00:15:27.110 --> 00:15:31.300
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't go alone. Riyo! 
Delmon's a tricky opponent!</font>

184
00:15:31.300 --> 00:15:33.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Stay close so that we can team up!</font>

185
00:15:33.370 --> 00:15:35.230
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">We can't lose another person!</font>

186
00:15:35.750 --> 00:15:42.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">There's another fan 
of Amo here. isn't there?</font>

187
00:15:40.940 --> 00:15:43.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}Eyes forward. Riyo! C'mon!</font>

188
00:15:44.060 --> 00:15:47.720
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Can't really trust any of them.</font>

189
00:15:47.720 --> 00:15:49.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Riyo! Eyes front!</font>

190
00:15:49.930 --> 00:15:52.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Pressure adjustment—Strong.</font>

191
00:15:57.120 --> 00:16:01.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Oh. big man. your weapon's so powerful!</font>

192
00:16:01.450 --> 00:16:04.660
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But don't bust Amo's house up too much!</font>

193
00:16:04.660 --> 00:16:07.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That was close... so close...</font>

194
00:16:04.660 --> 00:16:07.900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You'd better help with the fixing-up later!</font>

195
00:16:08.170 --> 00:16:10.430
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Focus. Riyo!</font>

196
00:16:13.550 --> 00:16:18.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Look! Can't tell who's on your side now. huh?</font>

197
00:16:18.360 --> 00:16:20.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You're scared. huh?</font>

198
00:16:20.800 --> 00:16:27.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo told you... everyone would have 
more fun if they just talked to Amo!</font>

199
00:16:27.670 --> 00:16:31.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Talk about romance is the first step to peace!</font>

200
00:16:31.520 --> 00:16:33.280
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's nuts.</font>

201
00:16:33.720 --> 00:16:36.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Rudo! Get up—</font>

202
00:16:33.720 --> 00:16:36.580
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Damn. Damn it.</font>

203
00:16:37.390 --> 00:16:38.500
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Rudo?</font>

204
00:16:39.120 --> 00:16:40.790
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What's going on?</font>

205
00:16:40.790 --> 00:16:43.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I thought I was on the Ground.</font>

206
00:16:44.640 --> 00:16:46.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What's going on here?</font>

207
00:16:46.170 --> 00:16:49.820
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'm on the Ground. On the Ground.</font>

208
00:16:50.860 --> 00:16:52.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I...</font>

209
00:16:53.190 --> 00:16:55.470
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Am I back in the Sphere?</font>

210
00:16:57.300 --> 00:16:59.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The hell's goin' on?</font>

211
00:17:03.430 --> 00:17:05.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What's that smell?</font>

212
00:17:05.860 --> 00:17:08.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's like... huh?</font>

213
00:17:09.220 --> 00:17:11.530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Smells so familiar...</font>

214
00:17:13.750 --> 00:17:17.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">How do you think memories work?</font>

215
00:17:18.780 --> 00:17:21.360
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Things you've seen... Things you've heard.</font>

216
00:17:21.360 --> 00:17:23.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">People you've spent time with.</font>

217
00:17:23.450 --> 00:17:26.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">All kinds of things turn into memories.</font>

218
00:17:29.440 --> 00:17:32.610
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But Amo thinks it's about smell.</font>

219
00:17:33.300 --> 00:17:39.950
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But if you won't talk about romance. 
you can smell a nostalgic scent.</font>

220
00:17:40.310 --> 00:17:42.740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Then maybe you'll feel 
a little more like romance!</font>

221
00:18:05.990 --> 00:18:07.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Chiwa...</font>

222
00:18:14.200 --> 00:18:18.210
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">He's lovely. I'll treasure him forever.</font>

223
00:18:18.650 --> 00:18:20.330
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You didn't...</font>

224
00:18:20.330 --> 00:18:22.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You didn't. though!</font>

225
00:18:22.320 --> 00:18:25.710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You threw him away!</font>

226
00:18:28.710 --> 00:18:31.130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You threw him away while I watched!</font>

227
00:18:33.800 --> 00:18:35.520
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's after Rudo now?</font>

228
00:18:36.530 --> 00:18:38.270
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">It's the same as with Delmon.</font>

229
00:18:38.270 --> 00:18:41.190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That wasn't a real betrayal.</font>

230
00:18:41.190 --> 00:18:43.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">She's showing him something...</font>

231
00:18:44.230 --> 00:18:46.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">with that power of hers.</font>

232
00:18:48.550 --> 00:18:50.850
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Showing him?</font>

233
00:18:51.900 --> 00:18:53.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">So silly.</font>

234
00:18:53.930 --> 00:18:57.030
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo doesn't show anyone anything.</font>

235
00:18:59.340 --> 00:19:02.390
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo just makes a smell.</font>

236
00:19:03.960 --> 00:19:09.930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo makes smells about happy times 
spent with people you love.</font>

237
00:19:09.930 --> 00:19:13.070
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maybe the smell is different for everyone.</font>

238
00:19:13.070 --> 00:19:16.870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">but everyone who smells it 
always starts to protect Amo!</font>

239
00:19:19.500 --> 00:19:21.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Amo said too much.</font>

240
00:19:22.110 --> 00:19:24.700
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I get it. Which means...</font>

241
00:19:25.500 --> 00:19:31.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">If we breathe in that smell. we'll start 
thinkin' you're a person we love?</font>

242
00:19:32.090 --> 00:19:35.090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Sounds like we'll be fine 
if we wear our masks. then.</font>

243
00:19:35.090 --> 00:19:38.290
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Thanks for givin' us that info.</font>

244
00:19:38.290 --> 00:19:43.450
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Besides. not all memories of people 
we love are necessarily happy ones.</font>

245
00:19:43.740 --> 00:19:48.220
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I wonder what would happen if it 
turned out to be someone we hated.</font>

246
00:19:49.100 --> 00:19:52.380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Maybe they'd wanna kill you!</font>

247
00:19:52.880 --> 00:19:56.250
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Well. we're just gonna take you out anyway.</font>

248
00:19:57.130 --> 00:19:59.760
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Stupid. You stupids!</font>

249
00:19:59.760 --> 00:20:03.770
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You must be crazy! So stupid!</font>

250
00:20:04.600 --> 00:20:06.910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Remember. Amo told you...</font>

251
00:20:06.910 --> 00:20:10.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">The memories are of <i>happy times</i>!</font>

252
00:20:12.320 --> 00:20:15.020
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Damn it. Damn it.</font>

253
00:20:15.470 --> 00:20:17.540
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You abandoned me.</font>

254
00:20:18.940 --> 00:20:22.670
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I hate you for that. So why...</font>

255
00:20:30.590 --> 00:20:36.100
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Why does the happy feeling 
seem so much bigger right now?</font>

256
00:20:40.720 --> 00:20:42.350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">What's going on? Hey!</font>

257
00:20:43.680 --> 00:20:46.810
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Stop it! Let me go!</font>

258
00:20:54.110 --> 00:20:55.690
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Rudo!</font>

259
00:20:55.690 --> 00:20:57.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Help me!</font>

260
00:21:06.850 --> 00:21:08.320
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">That hurt. dammit!</font>

261
00:21:08.320 --> 00:21:11.260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">You'll pay for hittin' me. Rudo!</font>

262
00:21:11.860 --> 00:21:16.170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Apostles. I'm not like I was back then.</font>

263
00:21:16.470 --> 00:21:18.600
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I've got real power now.</font>

264
00:21:18.600 --> 00:21:21.370
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Power so I don't have to lose anyone again...</font>

265
00:21:22.300 --> 00:21:26.990
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">And the power to kick all of your asses!</font>

266
00:21:27.690 --> 00:21:29.150
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Don't worry.</font>

267
00:21:33.030 --> 00:21:36.570
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll protect you. Relax.</font>

268
00:21:38.800 --> 00:21:40.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I'll beat them. For you.</font>

269
00:21:40.860 --> 00:21:41.860
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Follo?!</font>

270
00:21:42.550 --> 00:21:43.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Crush them!</font>

271
00:21:49.510 --> 00:21:52.110
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Looks like we miscalculated.</font>

272
00:21:53.760 --> 00:21:56.890
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">They were all too far gone.</font>

273
00:21:59.210 --> 00:22:02.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">I never wanted to use my 
instrument on a friend.</font>

274
00:22:07.540 --> 00:22:09.460
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">But I see I have no choice.</font>

275
00:22:10.305 --> 00:23:10.476
